{"tid":421054,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人識解黑魔法？","createTime":"2017-10-02T02:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T07:33:22.000Z","uid":55851,"like":7,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c0d55c75b669f5a93d444bc4a91337c9112eed7d","tid":421054,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:25:15.000Z","msg":"我有個親戚(女嘅)喺幾年前去左霍格華茲啲鬼地方度讀書，佢原本係住香港<br />\n<br />\n從此就一去不返，我近呢幾年先知原來我親戚比當地魔法流氓欺凌，以為佢麻瓜一個所以就好好恰，就施咗黑魔法落佢身上<br />\n想利用佢叫佢屋企人寄錢黎霍格華茲比條流氓洗<br />\n<br />\n聽講個流氓話邀請我親戚一齊去食野，點知出到去就施魔法搞佢<br />\n<br />\n曾經大家都好想救佢，但可能魔法施咗太耐，我親戚連去格離屋，都覺得好辛苦好想死，唔見個流氓唔得<br />\n<br />\n其他親戚都為呢件事煩緊，好憎個流氓咁樣拆散人地家庭，正仆街<br />\n<br />\n所以我想問你地識唔識/有無識人係識搞呢啲case"},{"pid":"b4d549a128fe148edc93943abac2e1397a5f0173","tid":421054,"uid":104256,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:43:36.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑？"},{"pid":"ae50faba5921c52130411f32e33f3164e9c3f292","tid":421054,"uid":129931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:46:06.000Z","msg":"我識白魔法"},{"pid":"6958ecf1d6aeff45ed72940a7154053e6bc31fb7","tid":421054,"uid":129931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我識白魔法</blockquote><br />\n仲有隻巫毒娃娃係屋企"},{"pid":"bee4e1e6e83f591cadfa7dc2dcf20873f5fb0357","tid":421054,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:00:59.000Z","msg":"個魔法好似幾勁，要係個流氓死左，我親戚先會得到解放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"827a4d456f10ff5ff381cc9088bb97564a8d5f39","tid":421054,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:03:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚好笑？</blockquote><br />\n世界咁大無其不有 好多嘢科學都解釋唔到啦 你未遇過唔代表冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405d9ab9507eefec925d27971add2453c902f9ef","tid":421054,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:04:41.000Z","msg":"有 ABCD係要講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先贏"},{"pid":"db126e1e5b76d4c515df01293e3ca6a24a9fa9af","tid":421054,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:04:47.000Z","msg":"麻瓜點去讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5adadd8eb75f35800a981872a99142bcf8c762","tid":421054,"uid":69522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:47:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疾疾護法現身</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：學過1年反黑魔法"},{"pid":"76a65a93868c714f30b601a5231664edff5df0a2","tid":421054,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:54:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疾疾護法現身</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：學過1年反黑魔法</blockquote><br />\n岩先召左隻雄鹿出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf3945016e943936711272a69a4be7c39158e85","tid":421054,"uid":23026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T06:49:37.000Z","msg":"哈哈，好笑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主收皮啦好冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ab6e99beeec70895a98c91483e0e11ec900d61","tid":421054,"uid":122601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T06:50:31.000Z","msg":"其實真係唔好笑"},{"pid":"594213225a8682ab2af069a41f146f6274ca73b6","tid":421054,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"真係唔撚怪得人話呢度係小學雞集中地"},{"pid":"ddc960eacebdf86fbce241f5db305ba7ef2d58a1","tid":421054,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:33:22.000Z","msg":"on9"}]}